quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  17,31,"Wota on warir Й“iЙ“Й“e mon Й“en kulol Й“illa=baasal, ko Menen arsikata Й“e, wonndude e mon ; pellet warugol Й“e ngol, wonii goopol manngol"
  17,32,"Wota on Й“atto jeeno ngon=fijrde nde, pellet Й—un wonii pankare e laawol bonungol"
  17,33,"Wata on waru wonkii, ki Allah harmini kin [warugol], si wonaa sabu hakkee. Mo tooГұaama waraama, Men waЙ—anii heftuЙ“e e makko Й“en doole wota non o fantin ka warugol. Pellet Kanko o wonii wallaaЙ—o"
  17,34,"Wata on Й“atto jawle Alyatiim, si wonaa Й“attagol Й“urngol moЖҙЖҙude, haa sagatalaaku makko timma ; humnee aadi ndin; pellet, aadi ndin wonii lannditoytee ndi"
  17,35,"Hunnee Й“etu ngun si on etay, manndikiron manndakke=peeson peese feewuЙ—e, ko Й—un moЖҙЖҙi, ko kaГұun Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude battane"
  17,36,"Wata a naatu e ko a anndaa fii mun. Pellet nanЙ—e Й—en, e giiЙ—e Й—en e Й“ernde nden, Й—iiЙ—oo fow wonii lannditoyteeЙ—i ka Makko"
  17,37,"Wata a yaaru ka leydi ГұaaЖҙa bunnga, ko fii pellet an a yulataa leydi ndin, a yottotaako pelle Й—en junndi=njuuteendi"
  17,38,"Й—in fow, bone majji on wonii aГұaaЙ—un ka Joomi maa"
  17,39,"ЖҠun, ko goЙ—Й—un e ko Joomi maaЙ—a wahayini faade e maa, immorde e Г‘eeГұal wata a waЙ—u reweteeЙ—o goo wonndude e Alla, sakko werleЙ—aa ka nder jahannama ko a felaaЙ—o raЙ—aaЙ—o"
  17,40,"E hara Joomi mon suЙ“ani on Й“iЙ“Й“e worЙ“e, O jogitoo immorde e malaa'ikaЙ“e Й“en rewЙ“e? Pellet, onon hiЙ—in wowlude konngol mawnungol"